Name: Extraction
Information: Tyler Rake, a fearless black market mercenary, embarks on the most deadly extraction of his career when he's enlisted to rescue the kidnapped son of an imprisoned international crime lord.

Name: Spenser Confidential
Information: When two Boston police officers are murdered, ex-cop Spenser teams up with his no-nonsense roommate, Hawk, to take down criminals.

Name: Eurovision Song Contest: The Story of Fire Saga
Information: When aspiring musicians Lars and Sigrit are given the opportunity to represent their country at the world's biggest song competition, they finally have a chance to prove that any dream worth having is a dream worth fighting for.

Name: The Outsider
Information: Investigators are confounded over an unspeakable crime that's been committed.

Name: The Hunt
Information: Twelve strangers wake up in a clearing. They don't know where they are, or how they got there. They don't know they've been chosen - for a very specific purpose - The Hunt.

Name: Dil Bechara
Information: The emotional journey of two hopelessly in love youngsters, a young girl, Kizie, suffering from cancer, and a boy, Manny, whom she meets at a support group.

Name: Sadak 2
Information: The film picks up where Sadak left off, revolving around the journey with a young girl who becomes an important character in the life of the protagonist, and the reason for him to stay alive.

Name: Birds of Prey: And the Fantabulous Emancipation of One Harley Quinn
Information: After splitting with the Joker, Harley Quinn joins superheroes Black Canary, Huntress and Renee Montoya to save a young girl from an evil crime lord.

Name: The Old Guard
Information: A covert team of immortal mercenaries are suddenly exposed and must now fight to keep their identity a secret just as an unexpected new member is discovered.

Name: Onward
Information: Two elven brothers embark on a quest to bring their father back for one day.

Name: Tenet
Information: Armed with only one word, Tenet, and fighting for the survival of the entire world, a Protagonist journeys through a twilight world of international espionage on a mission that will unfold in something beyond real time.

Name: Sonic the Hedgehog
Information: After discovering a small, blue, fast hedgehog, a small-town police officer must help him defeat an evil genius who wants to do experiments on him.

Name: Bloodshot
Information: Ray Garrison, a slain soldier, is re-animated with superpowers.

Name: Bad Boys for Life
Information: Miami detectives Mike Lowrey and Marcus Burnett must face off against a mother-and-son pair of drug lords who wreak vengeful havoc on their city.

Name: The Invisible Man
Information: When Cecilia's abusive ex takes his own life and leaves her his fortune, she suspects his death was a hoax. As a series of coincidences turn lethal, Cecilia works to prove that she is being hunted by someone nobody can see.

Name: Love, Death & Robots
Information: A collection of animated short stories that span various genres including science fiction, fantasy, horror and comedy.

Name: El Camino: A Breaking Bad Movie
Information: Fugitive Jesse Pinkman runs from his captors, the law and his past.

Name: Knives Out
Actors: ['Daniel Craig', 'Chris Evans', 'Ana de Armas', 'Jamie Lee Curtis']
Information: A detective investigates the death of a patriarch of an eccentric, combative family.

Name: Midsommar
Information: A couple travels to Sweden to visit a rural hometown's fabled mid-summer festival. What begins as an idyllic retreat quickly devolves into an increasingly violent and bizarre competition at the hands of a pagan cult.

Name: Portrait de la jeune fille en feu
Information: On an isolated island in Brittany at the end of the eighteenth century, a female painter is obliged to paint a wedding portrait of a young woman.

April 6th, 1917. As a regiment assembles to wage war deep in enemy territory, two soldiers are assigned to race against time and deliver a message that will stop 1,600 men from walking straight into a deadly trap.

Name: The Two Popes
Information: Behind Vatican walls, the conservative Pope Benedict XVI and the liberal future Pope Francis must find common ground to forge a new path for the Catholic Church.

Name: After Life
Information: After Tony's wife dies unexpectedly, his nice-guy persona is altered into an impulsive, devil-may-care attitude; taking his old world by storm.

Name: The Gentlemen
Information: An American expat tries to sell off his highly profitable marijuana empire in London, triggering plots, schemes, bribery and blackmail in an attempt to steal his domain out from under him.

Name: Crawl
Information: A young woman, while attempting to save her father during a category 5 hurricane, finds herself trapped in a flooding house and must fight for her life against alligators.

Name: Annabelle Comes Home
Information: While babysitting the daughter of Ed and Lorraine Warren, a teenager and her friend unknowingly awaken an evil spirit trapped in a doll.

Name: El hoyo
Information: A vertical prison with one cell per level. Two people per cell. One only food platform and two minutes per day to feed from up to down. An endless nightmare trapped in The Hole.

Name: Happy Death Day 2U
Information: Tree Gelbman discovers that dying over and over was surprisingly easier than the dangers that lie ahead.

Name: The Mandalorian
Information: The travels of a lone bounty hunter in the outer reaches of the galaxy, far from the authority of the New Republic.

Name: 6 Underground
Information: Meet a new kind of action hero. Six untraceable agents, totally off the grid. They've buried their pasts so they can change the future.

Name: Yesterday
Information: A struggling musician realizes he's the only person on Earth who can remember The Beatles after waking up in an alternate timeline where they never existed.

Name: The King
Information: Hal, wayward prince and heir to the English throne, is crowned King Henry V after his tyrannical father dies. Now the young king must navigate palace politics, the war his father left behind, and the emotional strings of his past life.

Name: The Lighthouse
Information: Two lighthouse keepers try to maintain their sanity whilst living on a remote and mysterious New England island in the 1890s.

Name: Jumanji: The Next Level
Information: In Jumanji: The Next Level, the gang is back but the game has changed. As they return to rescue one of their own, the players will have to brave parts unknown from arid deserts to snowy mountains, to escape the world's most dangerous game.

Name: Ready or Not
Information: A bride's wedding night takes a sinister turn when her eccentric new in-laws force her to take part in a terrifying game.

Name: Sex Education
Information: A teenage boy with a sex therapist mother teams up with a high school classmate to set up an underground sex therapy clinic at school.

Name: Brightburn
Information: What if a child from another world crash-landed on Earth, but instead of becoming a hero to mankind, he proved to be something far more sinister?

Name: Marriage Story
Information: Noah Baumbach's incisive and compassionate look at a marriage breaking up and a family staying together.

Name: Russian Doll
Information: A cynical young woman in New York City keeps dying and returning to the party that's being thrown in her honor on that same evening. She tries to find a way out of this strange time loop.

Name: Anna
Information: Beneath Anna Poliatova's striking beauty lies a secret that will unleash her indelible strength and skill to become one of the world's most feared government assassins.

Name: It Chapter Two
Information: Twenty-seven years after their first encounter with the terrifying Pennywise, the Losers Club have grown up and moved away, until a devastating phone call brings them back.

Name: Good Boys
Information: Three 6th grade boys ditch school and embark on an epic journey while carrying accidentally stolen drugs, being hunted by teenage girls, and trying to make their way home in time for a long-awaited party.

Name: Joker
Information: In Gotham City, mentally troubled comedian Arthur Fleck is disregarded and mistreated by society. He then embarks on a downward spiral of revolution and bloody crime. This path brings him face-to-face with his alter-ego: the Joker.

Name: Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood
Information: A faded television actor and his stunt double strive to achieve fame and success in the final years of Hollywood's Golden Age in 1969 Los Angeles.

Name: Velvet Buzzsaw
Information: A satire set in the contemporary art world scene of Los Angeles, where big money artists and mega-collectors pay a high price when art collides with commerce.

Name: Midway
Information: The story of the Battle of Midway, told by the leaders and the sailors who fought it.

Name: Us
Information: A family's serene beach vacation turns to chaos when their doppelgängers appear and begin to terrorize them.

Name: Glass
Information: Security guard David Dunn uses his supernatural abilities to track Kevin Wendell Crumb, a disturbed man who has twenty-four personalities.

Name: Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw
Information: Lawman Luke Hobbs (Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson) and outcast Deckard Shaw (Jason Statham) form an unlikely alliance when a cyber-genetically enhanced villain threatens the future of humanity.

Name: Gisaengchung
Information: Greed and class discrimination threaten the newly formed symbiotic relationship between the wealthy Park family and the destitute Kim clan.
